# Supporting Elements Inventory

- Status: `{{ inventory.status }}`

## Summary
- Figures: {{ summary.figures_count }}
- Tables: {{ summary.tables_count }}
- Citations: {{ summary.citations_count }}
- Bibliography mode: {{ summary.bibliography_mode }}

## Figures
{% if inventory.figures %}
{% for item in inventory.figures %}
- Figure {{ item.index }}: label=`{{ item.label }}` caption=`{{ item.caption_preview }}` lines={{ item.source_line_start }}-{{ item.source_line_end }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
- 无
{% endif %}

## Tables
{% if inventory.tables %}
{% for item in inventory.tables %}
- Table {{ item.index }}: label=`{{ item.label }}` caption=`{{ item.caption_preview }}` lines={{ item.source_line_start }}-{{ item.source_line_end }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
- 无
{% endif %}

## Citations
{% if inventory.citations %}
{% for item in inventory.citations %}
- Citation {{ item.index }}: command=`{{ item.command }}` keys=[{{ item["keys"] | join(", ") }}] line={{ item.source_line }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
- 无
{% endif %}

## Bibliography
- Mode: `{{ bibliography.mode }}`
- Resources:
{% if bibliography.resources %}
{% for item in bibliography.resources %}
  - {{ item }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
  - 无
{% endif %}
